creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
With over 40 games and more than 10.000 active players, elo is the perfect gaming app for you and your friends!

Play against elo players around the world or with your friends, family or workmates and everyone who enjoys game classics, word games, strategy games, dice games and new board games on the market.

Highlights on elo:

  • Chat with your opponents
  • Regularly new games
  • Up to 6 player games
  • Play turn by turn or live against each other
  • Climb to the first place in the leaderboard
  • Works on nearly every device - platform independent

    Our novelties:

  • Qwixx Blitz - the favorite dice game in a super fast version
  • Bingo - the ultimate challenge against the time and your opponent (4/20/18)
  • Ubongo - the original puzzle game with over 2 million sales worldwide (May)
  • Nmbr9 - an awesome tile-laying game in 3D (June)

    Our favorite games:

  • Dicetime - group your dice skillfully
  • High Sea Battle - Battleships on the high sea
  • Chess - turn by turn or as a blitz match
  • Sketch It! - for all drawing lovers

    Furthermore:

    Avalam, Cave of Doom, Wordblock, Three Jewels, Vortex, Beasty Bar, weekeewachee, Reversi, 4 in a row, WORDZ, Spot the Difference, Trippple, Germz, Order of Colors, Tic Tac Toe, Towers, Crooks out!

    elo - play together

    https://www.elo-games.com/

    We love games and we are passionate about the quality of our apps. Do you have ideas for new elo games? Is anything not working as expected? Please let us know right away:

    feedback@elo-games.com
descriptionShort: Play more than 35 built-in multiplayer games

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Thanks for your great feedback on elo. With your help we were able to crush many bugs of our first release. Enjoy improved notifications, a even more comprehensive layout of the challenges, the all new news area and many performance improvements. But as always: the best of elo are the games. In March we start two new challenges: one for those, who like dicing and another one for the word acrobats.

In March we start two new challenges: one for those, who like dicing and another one for the word acrobats.

title: elo - play together

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
With over 40 games and more than 10.000 active players, elo is the perfect gaming app for you and your friends!

Play against elo players around the world or with your friends, family or workmates and everyone who enjoys game classics, word games, strategy games, dice games and new board games on the market.

Highlights on elo:

  • Chat with your opponents
  • Regularly new games
  • Up to 6 player games
  • Play turn by turn or live against each other
  • Climb to the first place in the leaderboard
  • Works on nearly every device - platform independent

    Our novelties:

  • Qwixx Blitz - the favorite dice game in a super fast version
  • Bingo - the ultimate challenge against the time and your opponent (4/20/18)
  • Ubongo - the original puzzle game with over 2 million sales worldwide (May)
  • Nmbr9 - an awesome tile-laying game in 3D (June)

    Our favorite games:

  • Dicetime - group your dice skillfully
  • High Sea Battle - Battleships on the high sea
  • Chess - turn by turn or as a blitz match
  • Sketch It! - for all drawing lovers

    Furthermore:

    Avalam, Cave of Doom, Wordblock, Three Jewels, Vortex, Beasty Bar, weekeewachee, Reversi, 4 in a row, WORDZ, Spot the Difference, Trippple, Germz, Order of Colors, Tic Tac Toe, Towers, Crooks out!

    elo - play together

    https://www.elo-games.com/

    We love games and we are passionate about the quality of our apps. Do you have ideas for new elo games? Is anything not working as expected? Please let us know right away:

    feedback@elo-games.com
descriptionShort: Play more than 35 built-in multiplayer games

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Our Easter update comes with a really big Easter surprise: in the new tab "Rooms" you can create a private room for your family, friends, your workmates, your classmates, etc. In your private room you can chat and even offer games. appDetails.recentChangesHtml: The elo voice chat is finally here! Feeling closer together is hardly possible. Offer a game to your family or friends and when they gather in the waiting room, you can start a voice chat. While you are playing together, you can talk, comment your moves, negotiate, arrange revenges - as if you were sitting next to each other.

title: elo - play together

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
With over 40 games and more than 10.000 active players, elo is the perfect gaming app for you and your friends!

Play against elo players around the world or with your friends, family or workmates and everyone who enjoys game classics, word games, strategy games, dice games and new board games on the market.

Highlights on elo:

  • Chat with your opponents
  • Regularly new games
  • Up to 6 player games
  • Play turn by turn or live against each other
  • Climb to the first place in the leaderboard
  • Works on nearly every device - platform independent

    Our novelties:

  • Qwixx Blitz - the favorite dice game in a super fast version
  • Bingo - the ultimate challenge against the time and your opponent (4/20/18)
  • Ubongo - the original puzzle game with over 2 million sales worldwide (May)
  • Nmbr9 - an awesome tile-laying game in 3D (June)

    Our favorite games:

  • Dicetime - group your dice skillfully
  • High Sea Battle - Battleships on the high sea
  • Chess - turn by turn or as a blitz match
  • Sketch It! - for all drawing lovers

    Avalam, Cave of Doom, Wordblock, Three Jewels, Vortex, Beasty Bar, weekeewachee, Reversi, 4 in a row, WORDZ, Spot the Difference, Trippple, Germz, Order of Colors, Tic Tac Toe, Towers, Crooks out!

title: elo - play together

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
With more than 50 games for 2 and more players, elo is for everyone who likes classic games and likes to spend time with people who share this passion. Meet people with the same favorite games as you, exactly at your level. Open a room with friends or family and offer games, or join weekly tournaments for honor and trophies.

elo connects people

Like playing board games, elo bridges generations in a playful way and connects children with parents and grandchildren with grandparents. elo overcomes distance when the common game can no longer be played at the table. elo fits perfectly into your daily routine because you can make your moves whenever you want. That’s why our claim is “play together”.

elo is variety

When asked what our users value most about elo, we keep hearing “the variety”. Regardless of whether you want to focus and plan tactical moves, or want to continue a match you already started by a few turns while watching television, elo has lovingly designed games for all situations. Classic board games such as Nine man's morris, chess, checkers or go, dice games, word games, quiz games or even games that you used to play under the school desk.

elo has a simple pricing model

We have developed all our games ourselves with great attention to detail and optimized them for the mobile phone screen and one-handed operation. You can test elo extensively and, if you want, also play ad-supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time as well as a very affordable annual subscription.

elo is developed with love

We are enthusiastic about the quality of our app, which is completely developed in Germany with great attention to detail. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know right away:

feedback@elo-games.com
descriptionShort: Over 50 classic and board games for 2 and more players

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: In this version tournaments celebrate their premiere on elo. That means an even more intense playing experience. Every evening there is a tournament for a selected game. Participation is free and no ads will get in your way. The best ranked participants will win wonderful trophies for exhibition in their profile.

title: elo - play together

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
With more than 50 games for 2 and more players, elo is for everyone who likes classic games and likes to spend time with people who share this passion. Meet people with the same favorite games as you, exactly at your level. Open a room with friends or family and offer games, or join weekly tournaments for honor and trophies.

elo connects people

Like playing board games, elo bridges generations in a playful way and connects children with parents and grandchildren with grandparents. elo overcomes distance when the common game can no longer be played at the table. elo fits perfectly into your daily routine because you can make your moves whenever you want. That’s why our claim is “play together”.

elo is variety

When asked what our users value most about elo, we keep hearing “the variety”. Regardless of whether you want to focus and plan tactical moves, or want to continue a match you already started by a few turns while watching television, elo has lovingly designed games for all situations. Classic board games such as Nine man's morris, chess, checkers or go, dice games, word games, quiz games or even games that you used to play under the school desk.

elo has a simple pricing model

We have developed all our games ourselves with great attention to detail and optimized them for the mobile phone screen and one-handed operation. You can test elo extensively and, if you want, also play ad-supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time as well as a very affordable annual subscription.

elo is developed with love

We are enthusiastic about the quality of our app, which is completely developed in Germany with great attention to detail. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know right away:

title: elo - play together

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
elo is for everyone who likes classic games, board games, parlor games, card games or dice games, and all the great games we like to play around a table in the family or with friends.
 
elo connects people
 
Playing together is a wonderful way of spending time together. elo overcomes the distance, and if need be, the time too. Everyone forwards the match by a few moves when time allows. This is how you can stay in touch with friends or family.
 
elo is a variety of games
 
elo not only has selected beautiful games - all designed with attention to detail and optimized for your mobile gaming experience - but also a large selection. In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:
 
feedback@elo-games.com

title: eloo - bord games for two

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
elo is for everyone who likes classic games, board games, parlor games, card games or dice games, and all the great games we like to play around a table in the family or with friends.
 
elo connects people
 
Playing together is a wonderful way of spending time together. elo overcomes the distance, and if need be, the time too. Everyone forwards the match by a few moves when time allows. This is how you can stay in touch with friends or family.
 
elo is a variety of games
 
elo not only has selected beautiful games - all designed with attention to detail and optimized for your mobile gaming experience - but also a large selection. In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model

In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Tournaments are very popular on elo. Now we are happy to announce daily puzzles! Download the new elo and you're good to go. Every week we provide new daily puzzles in different games that you can play (or solve) whenever you like. Look forward to Wordle Solo, Ubongo, NMBR 9, Double, WordBlock and several more.

title: elo - board games for two

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
elo is for everyone who likes classic games, board games, parlor games, card games or dice games, and all the great games we like to play around a table in the family or with friends.
 
elo connects people
 
Playing together is a wonderful way of spending time together. elo overcomes the distance, and if need be, the time too. Everyone forwards the match by a few moves when time allows. This is how you can stay in touch with friends or family.
 
elo is a variety of games
 
elo not only has selected beautiful games - all designed with attention to detail and optimized for your mobile gaming experience - but also a large selection. In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:
 
feedback@elo-games.com
descriptionShort: Over 50 classic and board games for 2 and more players

title: elo - board games for two

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
elo is for everyone who likes classic games, board games, parlor games, card games or dice games, and all the great games we like to play around a table in the family or with friends.
 
elo connects people
 
Playing together is a wonderful way of spending time together. elo overcomes the distance, and if need be, the time too. Everyone forwards the match by a few moves when time allows. This is how you can stay in touch with friends or family.
 
elo is a variety of games
 
elo not only has selected beautiful games - all designed with attention to detail and optimized for your mobile gaming experience - but also a large selection. In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:
 
feedback@elo-games.com

title: elo - board games for two

creator: elo Games GmbH
descriptionHtml:
elo is for everyone who likes classic games, board games, parlor games, card games or dice games, and all the great games we like to play around a table in the family or with friends.
 
elo connects people
 
Playing together is a wonderful way of spending time together. elo overcomes the distance, and if need be, the time too. Everyone forwards the match by a few moves when time allows. This is how you can stay in touch with friends or family.
 
elo is a variety of games
 
elo not only has selected beautiful games - all designed with attention to detail and optimized for your mobile gaming experience - but also a large selection. In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:

In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:
 
feedback@elo-games.com
descriptionShort: Over 50 classic and board games for 2 and more players

title: elo - board games for two

creator: elo Friends GmbH
descriptionHtml:
elo is for everyone who likes classic games, board games, parlor games, card games or dice games, and all the great games we like to play around a table in the family or with friends.
 
elo connects people
 
Playing together is a wonderful way of spending time together. elo overcomes the distance, and if need be, the time too. Everyone forwards the match by a few moves when time allows. This is how you can stay in touch with friends or family.
 
elo is a variety of games
 
elo not only has selected beautiful games - all designed with attention to detail and optimized for your mobile gaming experience - but also a large selection. In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:
 
feedback@elo-games.com
descriptionShort: Over 50 classic and board games for 2 and more players

Playing together is a wonderful way of spending time together. elo overcomes the distance, and if need be, the time too. Everyone forwards the match by a few moves when time allows. This is how you can stay in touch with friends or family.
 
elo is a variety of games
 
elo not only has selected beautiful games - all designed with attention to detail and optimized for your mobile gaming experience - but also a large selection. In addition to the over 60 games, one is added every month. Our most popular games are Rummy, Una and Reducto. Our classics are Nine Men’s Morris, Checkers, Chess and Go. At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:
 
feedback@elo-games.com
descriptionShort: Over 50 classic and board games for 2 and more players

At elo there are dice games like TwentyOne or Qwixx, action games like Ubongo or Double, word games and more than just one Trivia Quiz.
 
elo is played with others
 
On elo you can take part in tournaments, play at two or more, as a whole family, as a group, on the go or at a party. Open a room on elo, chat, propose games, play series or start the voice chat, and the fun can begin.
 
elo has a simple pricing model
 
You can test elo extensively and, if you want, play permanently ad supported. But because we know that many of our users use elo for months and years, we offer a fair monthly subscription that can be canceled at any time or a particularly affordable annual subscription.
 
elo is developed with passion
 
We are proud of the quality of our app, which is developed with great attention to detail in Germany, where board games have a great tradition. Is something not working as expected? Please let us know:
 
feedback@elo-games.com
